# Claude Code Team System - Environment Configuration
#
# If ANTHROPIC_API_KEY is set in your shell (~/.bashrc, ~/.zshrc, etc.),
# the agents will use that key's credit balance instead of your Claude Code Pro plan.
# This causes "Credit balance is too low" errors.
#
# To fix: either unset it before running the team:
#   unset ANTHROPIC_API_KEY
#
# Or add it here with an empty value to override any shell-level setting:
#   ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
#
# Only set a real key here if you intentionally want to use API credits instead of Pro plan.
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=